{
  "texts": [
    "Evaluation of Music Generation Abilities.",
    "Our evaluation of musicality primarily depends on human judgment.",
    "Additionally, we have developed two specific metrics: a phrase-level repetition metric and a parsing success rate metric, aimed at assessing the structureness and format accuracy of the generated music.",
    "Furthermore, we introduce an average percentile score metric to gauge the models' controllability.",
    "We use the proposed MusicTheoryBench to evaluate our model and the baseline systems' music understanding abilities."
  ]
}